d": 1781850389, "replies": 30, "id": 1221525}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/7407/1a67/477_large.png?m=1439978846", "name": "editors", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/7407/1a67/477_normal.png?m=1439978846", "title": "编辑器", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/editors", "topics": 151, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Editors", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/7407/1a67/477_mini.png?m=1439978846", "stars": 214, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 477, "parent_node_name": "programming"}, "member": {"id": 496308, "username": "Zarhani", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Zarhani", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7fcd/13e3/496308_mini.png?m=1762129271", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7fcd/13e3/496308_normal.png?m=1762129271", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7fcd/13e3/496308_large.png?m=1762129271", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7fcd/13e3/496308_xlarge.png?m=1762129271", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7fcd/13e3/496308_xxlarge.png?m=1762129271", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7fcd/13e3/496308_xxxlarge.png?m=1762129271", "created": 1593074092, "last_modified": 1762129271, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "laminux29", "last_touched": 1781894414, "title": "vim 真的好用吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1221499", "created": 1781838263, "deleted": 0, "content": "我下过 vscode 的 vim 插件，也用过 vim 命令，但是感觉用起来非常得难受，也经常搞错当前是编辑模式还是命令模式，这东西用多了后真的会变得熟练吗？", "content_rendered": "<p>我下过 vscode 的 vim 插件，也用过 vim 命令，但是感觉用起来非常得难受，也经常搞错当前是编辑模式还是命令模式，这东西用多了后真的会变得熟练吗？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1781838263, "replies": 27, "id": 1221499}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 71658, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9714, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 289197, "username": "weiyunjun", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/weiyunjun", "website": "https://weiyunjun.com", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8823/36f6/289197_mini.png?m=1777951184", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8823/36f6/289197_normal.png?m=1777951184", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8823/36f6/289197_large.png?m=1777951184", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8823/36f6/289197_xlarge.png?m=1777951184", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8823/36f6/289197_xxlarge.png?m=1777951184", "created": 1517618393, "last_modified": 1777951184, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "drymonfidelia", "last_touched": 1781894385, "title": "前端界面比想象中复杂好多", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1221555", "created": 1781867910, "deleted": 0, "content": "刚接触 Vibe Coding 时就感觉前端比后端复杂好多，后端只需要不停按照需求优化性能就好了，有客观的测试数据，如果优化效果不符合预期就检查架构是否有改进的空间。总而言之就是流程可控。\r\n\r\n前端界面一开始完全不会，找类似软件学习，然后和 Codex 描述需求，各种细节瑕疵，花费很大精力改得差不多，身心俱疲，然后下一次改动又重复一遍这个流程。\r\n\r\n痛定思痛，反思流程问题，于是整理出前端文档，找 ChatGPT 网页端生成组件和布局的示意图，包含各种状态。再让 Codex 根据示意图和文档绘制界面，再修改文档修复 bug ，改完以后找 ChatGPT 重新生成最新版本的示意图。\r\n\r\n这个过程真的很漫长，因为端到端测试都要自己来，而且还不放心，还要再开一个窗口让 Codex review 代码。\r\n\r\n其实我之前尝试过 Claude Design 和 Claude Code 协作写前端，但细节有很多问题，Claude Code 也处理不好。我想请教一下大家，是前端本来就如此复杂，还是我的流程有问题导致如此繁琐？", "content_rendered": "<p>刚接触 Vibe Coding 时就感觉前端比后端复杂好多，后端只需要不停按照需求优化性能就好了，有客观的测试数据，如果优化效果不符合预期就检查架构是否有改进的空间。总而言之就是流程可控。</p>\n<p>前端界面一开始完全不会，找类似软件学习，然后和 Codex 描述需求，各种细节瑕疵，花费很大精力改得差不多，身心俱疲，然后下一次改动又重复一遍这个流程。</p>\n<p>痛定思痛，反思流程问题，于是整理出前端文档，找 ChatGPT 网页端生成组件和布局的示意图，包含各种状态。再让 Codex 根据示意图和文档绘制界面，再修改文档修复 bug ，改完以后找 ChatGPT 重新生成最新版本的示意图。</p>\n<p>这个过程真的很漫长，因为端到端测试都要自己来，而且还不放心，还要再开一个窗口让 Codex review 代码。</p>\n<p>其实我之前尝试过 Claude Design 和 Claude Code 协作写前端，但细节有很多问题，Claude Code 也处理不好。我想请教一下大家，是前端本来就如此复杂，还是我的流程有问题导致如此繁琐？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1781867910, "replies": 22, "id": 1221555}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c6bf/f625/1101_large.png?m=1751736810", "name": "copilot", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c6bf/f625/1101_normal.png?m=1751736810", "title": "GitHub Copilot", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/copilot", "topics": 375, "footer": "", "header": "来自 GitHub 的基于 AI 的结对编程工具 <a href=\"https://copilot.github.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Copilot</a>", "title_alternative": "GitHub Copilot", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c6bf/f625/1101_mini.png?m=1751736810", "stars": 371, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1101, "parent_node_name": "programmer"}, "member": {"id": 556606, "username": "Julaoshi", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Julaoshi", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4a0/452d/556606_mini.png?m=1771914979", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4a0/452d/556606_normal.png?m=1771914979", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4a0/452d/556606_large.png?m=1771914979", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4a0/452d/556606_xlarge.png?m=1771914979", "created": 1632304079, "last_modified": 1771914979, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "jowu598", "last_touched": 1781873518, "title": "GitHub copilot 重新恢复订阅了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1221510", "created": 1781843990, "deleted": 0, "content": "之前 4 月份下旬似乎不再接受新订阅了。今天试了下，发现能恢复了。虽然性价比比以前差了很多，但是我感觉 vs code 用起来还是最顺的，修改也最精准。准备先用个 $10 套餐试试。", "content_rendered": "<p>之前 4 月份下旬似乎不再接受新订阅了。今天试了下，发现能恢复了。虽然性价比比以前差了很多，但是我感觉 vs code 用起来还是最顺的，修改也最精准。准备先用个 $10 套餐试试。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1781843990, "replies": 18, "id": 1221510}]